RoboClaw Web-Controlled Robotic Claw
The project was Developed by Jeremy E. Blum <www.jeremyblum.com>
More info is available at http://jeremyblum.com/tag/roboclaw/

This is Open Source Hardware and Software Licensed via a Creative Commons Attribution Share-Alike License
http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/us/

The code is written in Spin for use on the Parallax propeller chip.  The chip communicates via serial with an PINK module (http://www.netburner.com/pink/index.html) to connect to the internet.  Solid-State Relays interface with the "EDGE" robotic claw to enable hardware control.